- Map pin click now opens a Google Maps InfoWindow with a peek (photo + title + neighborhood/BR/BA + price/rating + "View details →" button) instead of immediately navigating away. Preserves the chat session — anon users don't lose their conversation just to peek a listing.
- Power-user shortcuts preserved: Cmd/Ctrl-click + middle-click + Enter-on-keyboard still navigate directly. The branching is at the `clickHandler` level, not by intercepting the marker event globally.
