- Pin metadata extended in `ChatCanvas` to include `image`, `rating`, `bedrooms`, `bathrooms` (loose-typed today; will tighten when the audit's `RentalPin extends MapPin` typing improvement lands).
- **Bug fix in this change:** initial draft used `new mapsLib.Size(0, -8)` for the InfoWindow `pixelOffset`, but `Size` is in the `core` library, not `maps`. The throw was caught by the existing `map_init_failed` handler, dropping the user into the fallback pin list. Fixed by dropping the cosmetic offset (Google's default places the bubble above the anchor).

